com.differ.differcore.service

Class VersionServiceImpl

  • com.differ.differcore.service.VersionServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VersionService

    @Service
public class VersionServiceImpl
implements VersionService

    Implementation of interface VersionService interface.

    Service uses org.springframework.core.io.ResourceLoader from springframework to get access to file system. It look up all API version files in file system.

    See Also:
    interface VersionService
